-- U.K. Stocks Resume Advance; Rolls-Royce Gains, BAE Sinks
-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 2012-09-13T14:07:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-13/u-k-stocks-resume-advance-rolls-royce-gains-bae-sinks.html
U.K. stocks resumed an advance,
sending the FTSE 100 Index up 0.4 percent to 5,803.86 at 3:05
p.m. in London.  The gauge has swung between gains and losses more than 10
times today before the  Federal Reserve  releases a statement on
monetary policy after the close of trading.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
